As we all no a massive storm by the name of Hurricane Katrine ripped throught the Gulf coastal states puttin that whole area in a cry for help.......Thousands presumed dead Thousands still trapped on roof tops in the convention cent and in the super dome....they have been days wit out food and water violence has picked up in these areas....hundreds of people are dying before our eyes of dehydration, starvation and heat stroke....all they want is our help...they reach their hands out to us askin please help....just 1 drop of water please...they pray to God to help them....they r low on supplies....they need our help.....their proverty is in devistation....they are dying of diseases everyday this goes on.................

 

Lets lend a hand.....lend a hand to help our fellow brothers and sisters....if we were sufforing in hell today and we reached our hand out to the Lord and asked please one drop of water to sooth my thirst....i know in my heart he would help if he could he would extend his hand and put that one drop of water on our tounge.... Lets extend our hand and put a bottal of water in each one of those peoples hands......WWJD....What Would Jesus Do....remember that wat would our Savior do to help us.....extend your hand to reach these people in need  go to the website below or any other organization taking up money for the victims of Hurricane Katrina and donate at least a $1....a dollar can go a long way into saving someones life please help......I donated a dollar earlier this week please contribute into saving these peoples lives....thank you.........

go hear to make a donation http://www.wxii12.com/news/4919439/detail.html

or if you know of another foundation takin up money please go there and donate if you can.....the people in these devostaed areas would greatly appreciate it.....
